            No experiments yet. The first zone goes down on stage soon —
            watch this space, or better: be in the room.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="rp-footnote"><span class="accent">ⓘ</span> External uptime monitoring badge lands here in M3 (measured from outside, so it survives our outages).</div>
